title: Louie Christopher Wee
text:
I am a data analyst and researcher based in Kelowna, British Columbia.
I am currently studying Data Analytics and Marketing at Okanagan College.
I worked as a Research Officer at CTS Global Equity Group from 2015 to 2021, focusing on market sentiment, risk management, and the fundamental and technical analyses of global equity markets. My efforts contributed to generating alpha returns.
Explore my website to learn more!
